2.11 Index of Win32 names excluded from the Dylan libraries

2.11.2 A

The following Win32 names are excluded from the Functional Developer Win32 API libraries.

AccessResource, AllocDSToCSAlias, AllocResource, AllocSelector,
AnsiLowerBuff, AnsiNext, AnsiPrev, AnsiToOem, AnsiToOemBuff,
AnsiUpper, AnsiUpperBuff
